Health check API 
1.  API Endpoint - API/v1/checkServer
	This project includes an HTTP GET API endpoint at api/v1/checkServer. The endpoint allows you to check the server using an external service.

	Request

	Method: GET
	URL: https://sky-scrapper.p.rapidapi.com/api/v1/checkServer
	Headers

	X-RapidAPI-Key: Your RapidAPI Key (e.g., "6d6850fd54mshf80e48c90d5c180p177608jsn6773e7760d8b")
	X-RapidAPI-Host: RapidAPI Host (e.g., "sky-scrapper.p.rapidapi.com")

	==================
	using System.Net.Http.Headers;
	var client = new HttpClient();
	var request = new HttpRequestMessage
	{
		Method = HttpMethod.Get,
		RequestUri = new Uri("https://sky-scrapper.p.rapidapi.com/api/v1/checkServer"),
		Headers =
		{
			{ "X-RapidAPI-Key", "6d6850fd54mshf80e48c90d5c180p177608jsn6773e7760d8b" },
			{ "X-RapidAPI-Host", "sky-scrapper.p.rapidapi.com" },
		},
	};
	using (var response = await client.SendAsync(request))
	{
		response.EnsureSuccessStatusCode();
		var body = await response.Content.ReadAsStringAsync();
		Console.WriteLine(body);
	}
	===================

3. API/v1/flights/searchFlights
This project includes an HTTP GET API endpoint at api/v1/flights/searchFlights. The endpoint allows you to search for flights based on various parameters such as origin, destination, date, and more.

Request

Method: GET
URL: https://sky-scrapper.p.rapidapi.com/api/v1/flights/searchFlights
Query Parameters

originSkyId: The identifier for the origin location (e.g., LOND).
destinationSkyId: The identifier for the destination location (e.g., NYCA).
originEntityId: The entity identifier for the origin location (e.g., 27544008).
destinationEntityId: The entity identifier for the destination location (e.g., 27537542).
date: The date of the flight (e.g., 2024-02-20).
adults: The number of adult passengers (e.g., 1).
currency: The currency for pricing (e.g., USD).
market: The market for the flight search (e.g., en-US).
countryCode: The country code (e.g., US).
Headers

X-RapidAPI-Key: Your RapidAPI Key (e.g., "6d6850fd54mshf80e48c90d5c180p177608jsn6773e7760d8b").
X-RapidAPI-Host: RapidAPI Host (e.g., "sky-scrapper.p.rapidapi.com").

	=====================
	using System.Net.Http.Headers;
	var client = new HttpClient();
	var request = new HttpRequestMessage
	{
		Method = HttpMethod.Get,
		RequestUri = new Uri("https://sky-scrapper.p.rapidapi.com/api/v1/flights/searchFlights?originSkyId=LOND&destinationSkyId=NYCA&originEntityId=27544008&destinationEntityId=27537542&date=2024-02-20&adults=1&currency=USD&market=en-US&countryCode=US"),
		Headers =
		{
			{ "X-RapidAPI-Key", "6d6850fd54mshf80e48c90d5c180p177608jsn6773e7760d8b" },
			{ "X-RapidAPI-Host", "sky-scrapper.p.rapidapi.com" },
		},
	};
	using (var response = await client.SendAsync(request))
	{
		response.EnsureSuccessStatusCode();
		var body = await response.Content.ReadAsStringAsync();
		Console.WriteLine(body);
	}
